@NODE "A" "Why shall I crypt ?"

            The meaning of crypting
           »»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»
 Crypting (encoding) of data is a fine thing, with a vengeance if these are
 secret, and if they get over a detour (on which they might be seen from
 unauthorized persons) to their receiver (BBS's, Internet, other net's).
 Sure there are alot of ways to transmit data to a person (and ONLY to this
 person) although other people could see it. So you can hide your data
 or you can encode it (transform it using a sheme which is only known by
 the sender and the (REAL) receiver.)
 Sure there are ways to hide files into other files... But we prefer the
 encode-method (-> crypting).

@ENDNODE
@NODE "B" "Which role does the Crypt-o-mat play ?"

            Which role does the Crypt-o-mat play ?
           »»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»

 The Crypt-O-Mat is such a program with which you can crypt a sourcefile,
 with your personal secret-key into a desatination file.
 The algorythm Crypt-O-Mat uses is called @{"ADDITIVE CONGRUENTAL ALGORYTHM." link "Z" 0}
 Crypt-O-Mat uses 10 kilobytes of your FAST RAM.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "C" "And how shall I use it ?"

            Using the Crypt-O-Mat
           »»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»
           
 The Crypt-O-Mat is because of it's GUI very simple to handle. (Don't start
 all documentations like this ? ;) For the filerequester, the REQTOOLS.LIBRARY
 is used. But it's NOT necessary !! If it's not present, the filerequester
 option is disabled.
 
 - Chose a file with the requester by pressing the gadget (button) beside the
   Source-gadget. You also can enter the whole path directly into the
   Source-gadget. If you want to crypt a whole directory or a whole partition,
   then just enter the path. e.g DH0:work/very_secret_stuff , or Dh1:

 - To enter the destfile, go on just like the source-file. If you want that
   the source-file will be overwritten with the encoded one, then just enter
   nothing here. If you crypt a directory or a partition, you can't enter a
   destination ! The content of this gadget won't be noticed then.
   
 - Enter your 4 digit secret-key into the key-gadget. Take care that you (or
   the receiver) will not lose it. If you've chosen the overwrite option and you
   lost the secret key... THE DATA WILL BE UNRESTORABLE DAMAGED !!!!!
   
 - Press "Crypt" if you want to encode, "Decrypt" if you want to decode.
   Wait until the message "Crypting..." has changed into "Waiting..." !
   This means that Crypt-O-Mat has finnished. DON'T INTERRUPT Crypt-O-Mat !
   Longer crypting-times are normal when using the directory-crypt.

Example:
   
   If you want to crypt a file (Text.txt) in directory dh0:texts"
   SUPER-DUPER-SECURE ! Take a sentence like, "DO YOU LIKE PIZZA"
   (Attention: This is casesensitive !) Now crypt the file with DO, after that
   with YOU then with LIKE and at last with PIZZA.
   
   If you want to decrypt the file you have to type the sentence BACKWARDS...
   Enter PIZZA, press decrypt, LIKE ->decrypt, YOU ->decrypt and DO -> decrypt...
   Now you have decoded the file...
  
@ENDNODE
@NODE "D" "What do I need ?"
   
            What do I need for working with Crypt-O-Mat ?
           »»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»

 You need:               - One amiga with OS 1.2 or higer
                         - 10 kilobytes free fast-ram :)
                         - reqtools.library v38 (works without, too!)
                         - XEN.font in fonts: directory (included)
@ENDNODE
@NODE "E" "Cool features..."

            Cool features of Crypt-o-mat's
           »»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»
 
 - Does work although the reqtools.library isn't installed (only the
   file-requesters won't work!)
 - Gives CLEAR error-messages, not this "Runtime error -23" mumbo-jumbo !
 - 100% Assembler - 100% Speed (5 MB File in RAM: - 8 SEC !!! - 68030)
 - Source & dest seperated + overwirte mode...
 - Directorycrypting
 - Asks you if protect-bits are set if the file should be crypted... 
   If you answer yes, the protect bits will be set, after crypting !
 - Cool GUI with reqtools-filerequester !
 - german & english version
 
@ENDNODE
@NODE "F" "Normal features..."
            
            Normal features
           »»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»»
 - Crypt-o-mat uses the font XEN/9, that makes the GUI always looking good...
 - Crypt-o-mat uses only 10kb RAM
